channel.title: How do I change teleports?
channel.description:
How do I change name of teleports! I've been looking everywhere! Don't tell me to use search button... done that already.
Also what client should I use?
I want one with alot of items and stuff. :)

item.title: How do I change teleports?
item.dc:creator: @The_Reaper_X The Reaper X
item.description:
@The_Reaper_X wrote:

It’s the texthandler. Period.

And I don’t think he was asking what client he should use according to the teleports. I think he just wanted to know what client we suggest he uses to get a lot of items and stuff… as he said…

item.title: How do I change teleports?
item.dc:creator: @vic_08 Vic_
item.description:
@vic_08 wrote:

[quote=“SkillersDream, post:5, topic:236539”][quote author=vic 08 link=topic=312197.msg2488246#msg2488246 date=1223948023]

If Your Changing Name on Tele Tabs Its Texthandler.java
If Your Changing Name of command such as ::pk to ::teampk then its client.java.

For The Client We would have to know what source you use.

[/quote]
